{"tid":1322041,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個喺新城市廣場撞鬼經歷","createTime":"2019-07-15T23:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T15:25:17.000Z","uid":79382,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0e84de7fbe3cbc03082699d279090dd9b3c0dc","tid":1322041,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:58:02.000Z","msg":"就早幾個月，喺最底嗰層食完飯，<br />\n嗰陣都接近11點，啲舖頭閂晒咁滯，<br />\n想行返出空地搭電梯上火車站，<br />\n見到個廣場有幾個女仔喺度跳舞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋著晒白色裙，個樣仲要冇表情，眼神好空洞，<br />\n望落勁詭異 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n癡撚線，我同我個fd唔敢再望，急急腳上返樓上，<br />\n上到去忍唔住望多一眼，屌，班女仔唔撚見咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚇撚到我哋即刻狗衝過去火車站，<br />\n開始見到多啲人，個心先定返啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次諗返起都好撚心寒，<br />\n夜晚11點有人喺嗰度跳舞已經唔撚make sense，<br />\n仲要跳跳下突然影都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老老竇竇，自從嗰次之後，都冇再去過新城市行街，<br />\n仆街星期日發生單咁嘅嘢，<br />\n搞到我又諗返起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4523e4874adeaa71f8e6ed9ec57114cf63c055","tid":1322041,"uid":79382,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35132369cd27591ac509c1fa6b958732c2982b55","tid":1322041,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749b12ba3dd8c7f710d3ced266d1efc315b4cb14","tid":1322041,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35132369cd27591ac509c1fa6b958732c2982b55","tid":1322041,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}